  "title": "Engineering Manager (Shipyard)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Manage engineering deliverables within budget and schedule</li><li>Perform engineering detailed design and develop solutions to resolve engineering related issues</li><li>Lead design review meetings and integration efforts</li><li>Produce engineering and production drawings that comply with contract specifications and class rules</li><li>Offer Technical Oversight by providing technical guidance, rules, regulatory updates, and training to team members.</li><li>Active involvement in Project Management activities by providing assistance in day-to-day operations and managing resources to optimize manpower utilization.</li><li>Manage vendor relationships and ensuring proper integration with other vessel systems.</li><li>Ensuring compliance with relevant class standards, codes, and safety regulations, aligned with client's specification requirement</li><li>Cross-Functional Collaboration with internal functional teams e.g. Commercial & Projects, clients, design houses and contractor to meet project objectives. <a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=e70d8fb808afe0f5cfc14d5e57cc540233604864867bf1871b5f49cde6512b7dJmltdHM9MTc2NTE1MjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=253747b4-aea0-669f-31db-5575af0c67b4&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubXljYXJlZXJzZnV0dXJlLmdvdi5zZy9qb2IvZW5naW5lZXJpbmcvZW5naW5lZXJpbmctbWFuYWdlci0lRTIlODAlOTMtaHZhYy1waXBpbmctbWVjaGFuaWNhbC1zeXN0ZW1zLWRpcmVjdC1zZWFyY2gtYXNpYS1iOThlYmQ4ZjMwOGE3NjczZmYyMWRjZGY5ZWRkYTU5Yg&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=e70d8fb808afe0f5cfc14d5e57cc540233604864867bf1871b5f49cde6512b7dJmltdHM9MTc2NTE1MjAwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=253747b4-aea0-669f-31db-5575af0c67b4&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubXljYXJlZXJzZnV0dXJlLmdvdi5zZy9qb2IvZW5naW5lZXJpbmcvZW5naW5lZXJpbmctbWFuYWdlci0lRTIlODAlOTMtaHZhYy1waXBpbmctbWVjaGFuaWNhbC1zeXN0ZW1zLWRpcmVjdC1zZWFyY2gtYXNpYS1iOThlYmQ4ZjMwOGE3NjczZmYyMWRjZGY5ZWRkYTU5Yg&ntb=1\" target=\"_blank\" 